<plot>In the middle of the night a sudden noise wakes a man up. It's Sarah, his wife, next to him in bed. Sarah is snoring, so it's going to be pretty hard for him to get to sleep again. A possible solution is to hold her nose. It works, but only for a few seconds. She won't stop. While the man thinks of ways to stop the terrible noise, Sarah has some more tricks up her sleeve that guarantee her husband will become an insomniac.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?432865</url></doc>
